sheet.name: Striver SDE Sheet
sheet.description:
Striver SDE Sheet contains very handily crafted and picked top coding interview questions from different topics of Data Structures & Algorithms. These questions are one of the most asked coding interview questions in coding interviews of companies like Google, Amazon, Microsoft, Facebook, Swiggy, Flipkart, etc, and cover almost all of the concepts related to Data Structure & Algorithms.

Note :  Due to legal and compliance requirements of TakeUForward (TUF), Codolio has updated the links to mirror the latest official TUF sheets. We made sure that your progress and notes remain fully intact , only the external links are updated
